---
title: Shrimp and Sausage Gumbo over Basmati Rice
description: There’s no denying the special place Cajun cuisine holds in America’s culinary diaspora. Its mix of African, European, and Native American influences translates into larger-than-life flavors that come at you like a Mardi Gras parade. Such is the case in our adaptation of gumbo, the famous thick and hearty stew, which is brimming with smoked sausage, succulent shrimp, tender bites of bell pepper, and our zesty Cajun spice blend.
